{"tid":1017661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【紅館夢成真】自爆不是處男 30歲許廷鏗：我都有啲經歷嘅！","createTime":"2019-02-11T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T21:09:44.000Z","uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8751754c734b8946839b599f383437e7b0fc68","tid":1017661,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"3月23日，許廷鏗終於夢想成真，喺紅館舉行處男個唱《再見智慧齒演唱會》，海報上佢仲俾人咀到成口都係唇膏添！「好彩你知道係唇印，因為有啲人以為係剝完智慧齒之後流牙血，其實個唇印係源自阿Jan一句說話，佢話許廷鏗喺大眾心目中，應該仲係一個處男，佢話既然你成日希望有成長、成人禮嘅感覺，就用紅館嚟做呢個成人禮，好似萬二人同我一齊共度初夜咁樣，我嘅第一次。」<span style=\"color: red;\">咁唔知現實中嘅Alfred仲有冇初夜？「現實嘅初夜，其實我都已經三十歲，都有啲經歷嘅。」</span>咁會唔會請啲前度嚟睇？「確實最近有同其中一位前度聯絡過，佢知道我喺紅館舉行演唱會，都有恭喜我，但我就唔敢再問落去，究竟佢會唔會嚟睇？」 <br />\n<br />\nAlfred係行內嘅友誼先生，選擇嘉賓名單會唔會好困難？「本身都好想請好多人，就算唔係做嘉賓，都希望佢哋嚟睇，但有一位keep住喺唔同場合，無論公開或者私底下相處都有俾說話我聽嘅，就係鄭欣宜，佢keep住同我講，「有啲人未正式邀請我！」搞到我都要三思睇吓請唔請佢好？因為坦白講，好多同我經歷唔同關口嘅朋友都好想邀請到，好多都真係會嚟睇同支持，我諗呢啲人情債都唔知需要還到幾時。」開紅館騷前，唔知Alfred使唔使節食keep fit呢？「有嘅，最近都努力緊，我諗重點唔係話要瘦到點樣用嚟show off，反而係想喺台上嘅狀態同精神面貌都比較好。」不過，相信佢班fans，最想見嘅係佢嘅爆肌演出囉！「暫時未得，因為嗰日做完健身自拍，覺得自己好白，有啲線條不過太白，要諗吓方法，我又唔想打陰影，因為喺台上會好明顯，所以可能要曬吓燈，到時睇情況，睇吓露唔露啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653441_0?fbclid=IwAR0lyin0IzNswOpB1UaEJbrUD_cWvr70DxzV7HYlO0hRsLkPkk7Pqw7WHZY&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653441_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0lyin0IzNswOpB1UaEJbrUD_cWvr70DxzV7HYlO0hRsLkPkk7Pqw7WHZY%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu17M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=c8a9bf55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_653441_0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0lyin0IzNswOpB1UaEJbrUD_cWvr70DxzV7HYlO0hRsLkPkk7Pqw7WHZY%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook&h=f941e108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_653441_0?fbclid=IwAR0lyin0IzNswOpB1UaEJbrUD_cWvr70DxzV7HYlO0hRsLkPkk7Pqw7WHZY&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook</a>"},{"pid":"6003669c418c204f686ab21d3ccacb18db215b1c","tid":1017661,"uid":72195,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"30歲仲要咁靚仔，同你講係處，你都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1b16e9a424daea08d1aa90d355bf478b4ec434","tid":1017661,"uid":38456,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"joyce"},{"pid":"9cdad699560c181439b5bab12de44d4e0f712968","tid":1017661,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3385a090a087c9557c4b3f0e59e30c480ceeda38","tid":1017661,"uid":188396,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6003669c418c204f686ab21d3ccacb18db215b1c","tid":1017661,"uid":72195,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"30歲仲要咁靚仔，同你講係處，你都唔信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"咁佢係前邊破咗定後邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1da1dc4e1e36ac4cf40ba9085ba72f9a4000314","tid":1017661,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"屌原來係唇膏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eefb67b6f8d59b3d81076953cdc5f1261e9f2f5","tid":1017661,"uid":124372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"佢唔會痾屎同打丁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ad633431